為同一件事鬧交<br />\n又溝通唔黎<br />\n雙方既需求不對等時<br />\n即使仲幾中意對方都好<br />\n都會覺得對將來冇期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24feb616f9b58a8153822a8198dcb89176396bfd","tid":361742,"uid":56055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係咁諗，條女唔係，<br />\n佢死都唔肯放手</blockquote><br />\n分手呢d野唔係單方面既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔想分 係咁反省 認錯<br />\n但佢只係好強調係適唔適合既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢喊到豬頭咁我衰心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得拍拖覺得唔夾咁不如做返朋友啦，<br />\n佢就覺得無可能做返朋友，所以唔肯放手"},{"pid":"83243f0ff53de2ba3b8d63bd6665077b0c001aa8","tid":361742,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"未一齊已經覺得唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58af3986f44f16c942a283334d45591efad7a96f","tid":361742,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知道同佢冇將來<br />\n可能為同一件事鬧交<br />\n又溝通唔黎<br />\n雙方既需求不對等時<br />\n即使仲幾中意對方都好<br />\n都會覺得對將來冇期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果對方道歉 話會成長會改變<br />\n覺得就咁放棄 唔會覺得好可惜<br />\n既然仲鐘意 點解會咁堅持一定要分開<br />\n真係唔明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca881d1262b3a80bff388210e0baefb386c57c1","tid":361742,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係咁諗，條女唔係，<br />\n佢死都唔肯放手</blockquote><br />\n分手呢d野唔係單方面既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔想分 係咁反省 認錯<br />\n但佢只係好強調係適唔適合既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢喊到豬頭咁我衰心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得拍拖覺得唔夾咁不如做返朋友啦，<br />\n佢就覺得無可能做返朋友，所以唔肯放手</blockquote><br />\n我都唔想做朋友其實 但如果喊俾佢睇到<br />\n我覺得都唔好睇<br />\n係佢隔住個mon講做返朋友比較好<br />\n我起屋企都喊左好耐<br />\n我覺得呢世都未必再返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033c3100e404859d2962a7bc60f29ef5965a03dd","tid":361742,"uid":134161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"只可以話已經唔愛，其他都係藉口<br />\n如果仲愛 好多問題都已經唔係問題"},{"pid":"4b485d1409317a78f5514d0faf44f72e896b57b6","tid":361742,"uid":123578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只可以話已經唔愛，其他都係藉口<br />\n如果仲愛 好多問題都已經唔係問題</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}